  "keyFeatures": [
    "Browser-based video conferencing with no plugin required",
    "IFrame API for embedding meetings into any web application",
    "React Native SDK (@jitsi/react-native-sdk) for iOS and Android",
    "End-to-end encryption (E2EE) via WebRTC Insertable Streams",
    "Breakout rooms for splitting participants into sub-sessions",
    "Virtual backgrounds and blur using TensorFlow.js",
    "Server-side and local recording support",
    "Lobby / knocking moderation system",
    "AV moderation (mute/unmute control for moderators)",
    "Jitsi as a Service (JaaS) hosted deployment via 8x8",
    "JWT-based authentication and room access control",
    "Scalable Video Coding (SVC) via Jitsi Videobridge (SFU)",
    "Tile view, filmstrip, and large-video layout modes",
    "Live subtitles / transcription",
    "Polls, reactions, whiteboard, and chat with private messages"
  ],
